# pro1-full-html-css

A complete front-end project built using **HTML**, **CSS**, and **Sass**, with layout and responsiveness achieved using **Flexbox** and **CSS Grid**.

## 🚀 Features

- Fully responsive design
- Clean HTML & modular CSS structure
- Sass support with variables and nesting
- Image sections and visual content
- Custom header with background image and overlay text
- About section
- Product kits section
- Contact form

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- Sass (SCSS)
- Flexbox
- CSS Grid

